Richard W. WOODS, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 19722. United States Court of Appeals Ninth Circuit. April 19, 1965. Wilson & Wilson, Anchorage, Alaska, James K. Tallman, Anchorage, Alaska, for appellant. Richard L. McVeigh, U. S. Atty., H. Russell Holland, Asst. U. S. Atty., Anchorage, Alaska, for appellee.

Before POPE, BROWNING and DUN-IWAY, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

In this matter we find no error in the record and accordingly the judgment is affirmed.
